OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FA London council said it has taken
OL,8,Flegal action against building owners
OL,9,Fto demand they remove Grenfell-style
OL,10,Fcladding in what it described as the
OL,11,Ffirst case of its kind.
OL,13,FTower Hamlets Council said it had
OL,14,Fsecured a remediation order requiring
OL,15,Fthe owners of a high-rise building in
OL,16,FStepney, in the east of the capital,
OL,17,Fto remove its aluminium composite
OL,18,Fmaterial (ACM) cladding.
