OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FThe council said it is the first local
OL,8,Fauthority in the country to bring a
OL,9,Flegal action of this kind against a
OL,10,Ffreeholder of a private building.
OL,12,FThe Grenfell Tower Inquiry concluded
OL,13,Fthat the principal reason flames shot
OL,14,Fup that building in June 2017 so
OL,15,Fquickly was the combustible ACM
OL,16,Fcladding with polyethylene core which
OL,17,Facted as a "source of fuel".
