OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FExecutive Mayor of Tower Hamlets,
OL,8,FLutfur Rahman, said: "It is shocking
OL,9,Fthat seven years after the devastating
OL,10,FGrenfell Tower fire there are still
OL,11,Fhigh-rise buildings clad in ACM in
OL,12,Fthis country.
OL,14,F"I believe everyone deserves to live
OL,15,Fin a safe and secure home in Tower
OL,16,FHamlets and this action proves we will
OL,17,Fdo everything within our power to get
OL,18,Fthis.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
