OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,F"I am proud of what we have achieved,
OL,8,Fand it is due to the hard work and
OL,9,Fdedication of officers. This is the
OL,10,Ffirst action of this kind, but it will
OL,11,Fnot be the last.
OL,13,F"We are taking this approach with
OL,14,Fother private building owners who are
OL,15,Ffailing to remove dangerous cladding
OL,16,Ffrom their buildings and we expect to
OL,17,Fsecure more orders in the near future."
