OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FThe council said the order requires
OL,8,Fthe building owners - which it said it
OL,9,Fis not naming - to replace ACM
OL,10,Fcladding and combustible insulation,
OL,11,Fand install new cavity barriers.
OL,13,FIt said failing to do so within a set
OL,14,Ftimeframe could see the owners face
OL,15,Fjail or an unlimited fine through the
OL,16,Fcounty court.
