OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FTower Hamlets said it used powers
OL,8,Funder the Housing Act 2004 and
OL,9,FBuilding Safety Act 2022 and secured
OL,10,Fagreement on the order on November 18,
OL,11,Fhaving applied to the First-Tier
OL,12,FTribunal Property Chamber.
OL,14,FWhile campaigners welcomed the
OL,15,F"positive" development for residents
OL,16,Fof the building affected by the order,
OL,17,Fthey warned that "piecemeal legal
OL,18,Faction on a building-by-building basis
OL,19,Fin regions across the country will not
OL,20,Fdeliver the real change" needed.
