OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FEnd Our Cladding Scandal also
OL,8,Fquestioned whether the costs of any
OL,9,Fwork carried out could end up being
OL,10,Fpassed to residents in the form of
OL,11,F"huge bills in their next service
OL,12,Fcharge demand".
OL,14,FThe campaign group said it remains
OL,15,F"deeply concerned" that the
OL,16,FGovernment's recently announced plan
OL,17,Fto address the problem of buildings
OL,18,Fstill clad in dangerous materials
OL,19,F"will fail to get a grip of this
OL,20,Fcrisis".
