OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FEarlier this week, the Government said
OL,8,Fbuilding owners who fail to remove
OL,9,Fdangerous cladding could face jail.
OL,11,FThe Government acknowledged there
OL,12,Fcould be up to 7,000 buildings in
OL,13,FEngland with dangerous materials that
OL,14,Fhave not yet been identified, while
OL,15,Fprogress on remediation work on high-
OL,16,Frises with known issues has been too
OL,17,Fslow.
