OL,3,CTower Hamlets Council takes legal
OL,4,Caction against building owners over
OL,5,Ccladding
OL,7,FThe remediation acceleration plan
OL,8,Fmeans that, by the end of 2029, all
OL,9,Fbuildings over 59ft (18m) tall with
OL,10,Funsafe cladding that are on a
OL,11,FGovernment scheme will have been
OL,12,Fremediated.
OL,14,FBy then, buildings over 36ft (11m)
OL,15,Ftall with unsafe cladding will either
OL,16,Fhave been remediated or have a date
OL,17,Ffor completion, with landlords liable
OL,18,Ffor tough penalties if they fail to
OL,19,Fcomply.
